  m_Name: Part8
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - You returned? In one piece?
  - "Sorry, I didn\u2019t mean to sound so surprised. You\u2019re so little\u2026
    and the last apprentice\u2026 ahem"
  - Anyway, with your ingredients, hop your way up to the cauldron.
  - "If you fall in, I won\u2019t fish you out. It takes eons for my fur to dry."
  - Drag and drop your ingredients and giggle water into the cauldron to craft your
    potion.
  - "When you\u2019re done, come over here and serve it to me"
